{"tid":235344,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"依家先學彈鋼琴好唔好？","createTime":"2017-05-09T02:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T21:37:05.000Z","uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"415b65fc9c37f7cbe8cb6462e2ac5148b566c65d","tid":235344,"uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"十九歲，屋企冇琴，如果要學就要打兼職儲錢買部電子琴。好鍾意蕭邦啲歌，ballade no1 in g minor 同 fantasie impromtu, spring waltz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但難到仆街，無三年都應該彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想學樣野可以比我發洩下情感，唔開心或開心都可以彈下咁，但先前學樂器全部都三分鐘熱度。想趁考完dse學返樣野，出唔出手好？"},{"pid":"4fd0da5928535d48b7193c0278cceb1da8f1be85","tid":235344,"uid":68002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"你都話三分鐘熱度 唔好浪費錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e72db3e99c91427d7ba75b0c62b8580d8429b87","tid":235344,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我今年都係19<br />\n好鐘意Chopin op64好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前細個有學 而家買咗部琴學返<br />\n學琴冇話咩幾歳學先好<br />\n你肯花時間既話，Chopin 啲曲一定都彈到"},{"pid":"886e89714e94f47072718482f55239a01e7fabe8","tid":235344,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"電子琴唔好 你會學壞個力度同彈法 養成唔好既習慣<br />\n你想去到彈到Chopin既程度 應該要買鋼琴"},{"pid":"bdce2496b29a74f3aa0d13de6372b5cc7553e304","tid":235344,"uid":37623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"我女友22歲學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db008664adafb9d501f9bb047d3963b7a29dd09","tid":235344,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十九歲，屋企冇琴，如果要學就要打兼職儲錢買部電子琴。好鍾意蕭邦啲歌，ballade no1 in g minor 同 fantasie impromtu, spring waltz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但難到仆街，無三年都應該彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想學樣野可以比我發洩下情感，唔開心或開心都可以彈下咁，但先前學樂器全部都三分鐘熱度。想趁考完dse學返樣野，出唔出手好？</blockquote><br />\n我都係差唔多年紀學<br />\n學左半年<br />\n電子琴彈唔到蕭邦<br />\n但你頭幾年應該都去唔到呢個程度<br />\n<br />\n到時先買真琴<br />\n<br />\n（個人經驗，自學唔撚得掂，浪費左半年，一學就揾老師好啲）"},{"pid":"5509e35f261479ee7962dd613f840f43a44482a3","tid":235344,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"我屋企有琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47e60bb0ec2d73a48bb9c9932cb80e47d8fdee6","tid":235344,"uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企有琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bbdf1453e4102a411538e8398901dad2baaf1c","tid":235344,"uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十九歲，屋企冇琴，如果要學就要打兼職儲錢買部電子琴。好鍾意蕭邦啲歌，ballade no1 in g minor 同 fantasie impromtu, spring waltz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但難到仆街，無三年都應該彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想學樣野可以比我發洩下情感，唔開心或開心都可以彈下咁，但先前學樂器全部都三分鐘熱度。想趁考完dse學返樣野，出唔出手好？</blockquote><br />\n我都係差唔多年紀學<br />\n學左半年<br />\n電子琴彈唔到蕭邦<br />\n但你頭幾年應該都去唔到呢個程度<br />\n<br />\n到時先買真琴<br />\n<br />\n（個人經驗，自學唔撚得掂，浪費左半年，一學就揾老師好啲）</blockquote><br />\n又無理由一開波就叫屋企埋坐地嗰啲&hellip;"},{"pid":"98ccf0e3593ebce96742efbbeb0e972b334297f2","tid":235344,"uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電子琴唔好 你會學壞個力度同彈法 養成唔好既習慣<br />\n你想去到彈到Chopin既程度 應該要買鋼琴</blockquote><br />\n感覺膠啲同輕力啲"},{"pid":"708fdda1f67dc533be8cab413de8bffc00f3704f","tid":235344,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十九歲，屋企冇琴，如果要學就要打兼職儲錢買部電子琴。好鍾意蕭邦啲歌，ballade no1 in g minor 同 fantasie impromtu, spring waltz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但難到仆街，無三年都應該彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想學樣野可以比我發洩下情感，唔開心或開心都可以彈下咁，但先前學樂器全部都三分鐘熱度。想趁考完dse學返樣野，出唔出手好？</blockquote><br />\n我都係差唔多年紀學<br />\n學左半年<br />\n電子琴彈唔到蕭邦<br />\n但你頭幾年應該都去唔到呢個程度<br />\n<br />\n到時先買真琴<br />\n<br />\n（個人經驗，自學唔撚得掂，浪費左半年，一學就揾老師好啲）</blockquote><br />\n又無理由一開波就叫屋企埋坐地嗰啲&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n數碼琴"},{"pid":"f70466b58d75d34c097e2f208d89cfe4a7a2f8d5","tid":235344,"uid":43424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我今年都係19<br />\n好鐘意Chopin op64好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前細個有學 而家買咗部琴學返<br />\n學琴冇話咩幾歳學先好<br />\n你肯花時間既話，Chopin 啲曲一定都彈到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx巴打"},{"pid":"b5ad147e37ffef0f44f16f3523b16582ee705a1a","tid":235344,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企有琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋼琴萬幾蚊買番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a964485382bb9b6429ed2403ea4e263539848a65","tid":235344,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十九歲，屋企冇琴，如果要學就要打兼職儲錢買部電子琴。好鍾意蕭邦啲歌，ballade no1 in g minor 同 fantasie impromtu, spring waltz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但難到仆街，無三年都應該彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\